v4.4 (2025-10-30)
  * added -ttl option to set time-to-live of TCP packets
  * fix autoconf issues

v4.3 (2025-10-29)
  * Support 'nosu' feature on linux
  * try to use '/bin/bash -login' as the default shell if none specified, or fallback to '/bin/sh -l'
  * support compiling with fortify-source, stackprotect and other 'hardening' compile options
  * bundle with libUseful-5.62

v4.2 (2019-07-19)
  * Allow a command *and arguments* to be supplied in the '.auth' file against a user.

v4.1 (2019-03-27)
  * Allow choice between system-installed libUseful or bundled version

v4.0 (2019-01-29)
  * changes to allow running entire app as a non-root user

v3.0 (2018-01-17)
  * TLS/SSL support (port 992) added.
  * bugfix for backspacing before start of input string
  * fix warnings with gcc compile related to LaunchPtyFunc

v2.0 (2017-12-19)
  * session config and namespace containers support added.

v1.0 (2016-01-06)
  * initial release
